	<h1 class="mb-4">Manifesto</h1>

	<div>

		<p>In&nbsp;2021, Yuri Milner published some of&nbsp;his ideas in&nbsp;a&nbsp;book, <strong>Eureka Manifesto: the Mission for Our Civilization</strong>.</p>
		<p>The manifesto gives his perspective on&nbsp;humanity&rsquo;s place in&nbsp;the Universe, the mission it&nbsp;entails, and the future we&nbsp;could be&nbsp;part of&nbsp;if&nbsp;we&nbsp;embrace this mission.</p>
		<p>You can read, listen to&nbsp;or&nbsp;download the book for free at&nbsp;<a href="https://yurimilnermanifesto.org/" target="_blank">yurimilnermanifesto.org</a>.</p>

	</div>

